The paper focuses on building a best-answer prediction model for technical Q&A sites, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). However, since the paper deals with text classification and information retrieval tasks, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The other sub-categories are also relevant because they involve machine learning and software engineering aspects of the problem.
